description:
I love learning new things and new ways of creating art.  Hence my very eclectic creations page and this series of paper craft /paper quilling projects.  My son encouraged me to not edit the project, but rather simply let a photo of it speak for its self. 

So I will do a drop and burn and see how it goes.  I will drop 50 and burn the leftovers and see what we have left in the end.
